{"tid":1361523,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)城市獵人 詭屋驚凶實錄/厲陰宅1-2","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T21:13:24.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ce0f3bdd3187d4239d2db270fbfb934d38f42b","tid":1361523,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=cf7a5f3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=594512a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=347e093f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e1/Nicky_Larson_et_le_Parfum_de_Cupidon.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe1%2FNicky_Larson_et_le_Parfum_de_Cupidon.jpeg&h=ce809c55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/1f/Conjuring_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F1f%2FConjuring_poster.jpg&h=e4680cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e2/The_Conjuring_2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe2%2FThe_Conjuring_2_Poster.jpg&h=7175e393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.孟波是被人稱「城市獵人」的私家偵探，他的個性幽默、正義、好色，擅長處理各種的棘手任務，深受信賴。有天一名神祕委託人交付一項危險任務，要他保護神奇的愛情靈藥「邱比特香水」，這種香水會讓人性慾大開，孟波天不怕地不怕，決定接受委託，誰知香水卻被有心人士偷走，孟波必須在47小時之內找回香水，否則天下將會「性事」大亂&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.1971年，美國羅德島州哈維爾，佩倫一家七口搬進了一棟郊區大宅，一家之主羅傑與妻子卡洛琳、和五個女兒&mdash;安卓莉亞、南希、克莉絲汀、辛蒂與愛普原本對新房子充滿期待，但不到幾天就覺得這棟新房子越來越不對勁；寵物狗在搬進去的第二天就神秘死去、所有的鐘全部停在淩晨三點零七分、房子每當夜裏都會飄來一股腐爛屍臭、所有的門在夜裏會頻繁開了又關、卡洛琳的身上頻繁會出現不該存在的淤青、克莉絲汀睡覺時老是覺得有人在抓她的腳、有夢遊症的辛蒂睡著時會用頭不停地撞擊一個老櫥櫃、而愛普在寵物狗死後不停地在跟一個叫羅伊的小孩說話..<br />\n<br />\n3.1976年，超自然現象探究者艾德與蘿琳&middot;華倫夫婦辦理了「阿米蒂維爾凶宅事件」，協助堪稱屋子裏發生了多起靈異事件的盧茲一家，來確認該屋子是否在兩年前發生了一場慘烈的血洗事件：一個名叫小羅納德&middot;迪菲歐殘忍在屋子裏殺光了他的家人後，在法庭上稱自己遭魔鬼附身而被迫殺死家人，最後沒被法官採信而被判處連續六個終身監禁。蘿琳運用自己與生俱來的陰陽眼來探查屋子各處時<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=2aab1237\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0CKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=9c92688a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be40fa67617cb00ccaa3d7321695b0438aff89a","tid":1361523,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5143bd329be3a6807e257a9094c0a8cb0ddb4ef7","tid":1361523,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:40:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要！唔該幫手推啊！！推得好辛苦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad5b05985dff34d0fa843d9bebb6c2d3b4936826","tid":1361523,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142cc8be5e577e0ff693a5df877ddca14bcffeba","tid":1361523,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd0bc74f96f8e601b0108b355ae81ba50c1602a","tid":1361523,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbd6639e54c22b7ba7e3ee769072cd3f36fbd0a","tid":1361523,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T20:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset